  "titles": "Veteran Tactical Squad",
  "lore": "Every chapter and company within the Space Marine Legions contains a cadre of experienced veteran warriors. In some Legions, this will often be those who have served since the early days of the Great Crusade, while in those whose tactics draw more attrition, it may simply be those warriors who refuse to succumb to the brutality of their methodology of war. Many of these units will be permitted to carry specialist or more dangerous or rare weaponry, allowing them to apply deadly firepower where it is required, and setting an example to their less-experienced brethren.",
